## ğŸ“˜ Sample Wireshark Filter

To detect FTP brute force:
```wireshark
ftp.request.command == "USER" || ftp.request.command == "PASS"
```

To detect DNS tunneling:
```wireshark
dns.qry.name contains "."
```

